  "instructions": [
    "Place a cedar plank over medium heat until it smokes, then set aside.",
    "Toast the bread slices on the cedar plank or a pan until golden, about 2 minutes per side.",
    "Mash the avocado in a bowl and stir in the softened vegan butter until creamy.",
    "Add the diced tomato, cilantro, lime juice, white wine, apple cider vinegar, oregano, smoked paprika, sea salt, and black pepper to the avocado mixture and combine gently.",
    "Let the mixture rest for 2 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Spread the avocado toast mixture evenly over each toasted bread slice.",
    "Drizzle a small amount of vegan butter on top for extra richness.",
    "Serve immediately on the cedar plank for a rustic presentation."
